                        "utilityType":  "control",
                        "description":  "Animate eligible nonmagical unattended Huge-or-smaller objects within 120 feet for up to 1 minute with concentration. Object size counts against your spellcasting ability modifier limit, each object becomes an allied Construct that shares your initiative, you can command any within 500 feet as a Bonus Action, uncommanded objects Dodge and avoid harm, and each object reverts at 0 Hit Points with excess damage carrying over.",
